Arthur Donaldson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Donaldson_(actor) 0 Arthur Donaldson (5 April 1869 – 28 September 1955), was a Swedish-American actor. He appeared in 71 films between 1910 and 1934. Arthur_Donaldson ( 5_April_1869 – 28_September_1955 ) , was a_Swedish-American_actor . He appeared in 71_films between 1910_and_1934 .
